msgctxt " 	 		60	500	440"
msgid "So what do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	210	746	536"
msgid "As I'm sure you're already aware, my partner\\r\n"
"and I are here on behalf of the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	106	907	801"
msgid "Chairman Dojima is in Fukuoka on official business."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	144	1063	919"
msgid "And we've been tasked with keeping him safe\\r\n"
"by the chief of headquarters, Aoyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	73	1141	1068"
msgid "Head of his own family,\\r\n"
"and assistant to the chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	71	1219	1148"
msgid "My name is Morinaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	105	1345	1240"
msgid "And this is my junior associate, Aizawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1420	1360"
msgid "Spare me the introductions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	108	1538	1430"
msgid "What did you drag me here to ask about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1640	1580"
msgid "Chairman Dojima's whereabouts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60ｆ以下です	　	　	46	1724	1678"
msgid "His whereabouts?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	70	1795	1725"
msgid "Yes. You see, last night..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	171	1971	1800"
msgid "The chairman met Patriarch Madarame of the\\r\n"
"Yamagasa Family in Nagasugai for alliance talks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	183	2171	1988"
msgid "The negotiations themselves proceeded unimpeded,\\r\n"
"but we lost track of the chairman directly after."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	122	2360	2238"
msgid "At the end of the meeting,\\r\n"
"Chairman Dojima went off alone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	84	2447	2363"
msgid "And was last seen getting into a taxi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	180	2648	2468"
msgid "We attempted to follow him by car,\\r\n"
"but weren't familiar enough with the Fukuoka roads."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	112	2766	2654"
msgid "In the end, we regrettably lost sight\\r\n"
"of the chairman's taxi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	141	2966	2825"
msgid "We cross-checked the taxi's license plate number\\r\n"
"with the Road Transport Bureau, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	111	3079	2968"
msgid "And found the car was registered\\r\n"
"to a Nagasu Taxi Company."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	166	3250	3084"
msgid "Not long after, we determined that\\r\n"
"the driver's name was Taichi Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	152	3458	3306"
msgid "But we have no reason to believe\\r\n"
"the chairman knew anyone by that name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	143	3608	3465"
msgid "It only seemed proper we came\\r\n"
"to meet this mysterious Taichi Suzuki-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	119	3728	3609"
msgid "So we waited until you\\r\n"
"eventually showed your face."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	176	3981	3805"
msgid "It did seem strange. The chairman intentionally\\r\n"
"chose a taxi in the middle of the queue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	95	4084	3989"
msgid "I didn't see what could compel him to do that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	4160	4100"
msgid "But I have an idea now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	166	4399	4233"
msgid "I'd never have imagined the driver was in fact\\r\n"
"Kazuma Kiryu-san, fourth chairman of the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	85	4497	4412"
msgid "I'm still in disbelief,\\r\n"
"to be honest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	4609	4549"
msgid "You have the wrong guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	175	4852	4677"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Do you know where\\r\n"
"Chairman Dojima is or not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	157	5086	4929"
msgid "I took a passenger on the highway,\\r\n"
"then dropped him off back near Nagasugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	5199	5139"
msgid "That's all I've got for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	5308	5248"
msgid "Is that truly it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	5405	5345"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	5689	5629"
msgid "Now are we done here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	71	5769	5698"
msgid "I have a shift to get to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	77	5863	5786"
msgid "So that's how it is, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	155	6075	5920"
msgid "You'd really abandon Chairman Dojima\\r\n"
"without so much as batting an eye?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60ｆ以下です	　	　	56	6162	6106"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60ｆ以下です	　	　	52	6215	6163"
msgid "You heard me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	130	6346	6216"
msgid "This is a pivotal moment for the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	65	6446	6381"
msgid "That's why we've come to Fukuoka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	129	6605	6476"
msgid "The chairman vanishing at a time\\r\n"
"like this is no insignificant matter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	127	6761	6634"
msgid "There could have been an\\r\n"
"accident, or worse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	154	6978	6824"
msgid "And yet, you don't seem even\\r\n"
"the slightest bit concerned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	100	7112	7012"
msgid "You'd hang the chairman out\\r\n"
"to dry like he was nothing to you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	7195	7135"
msgid "Aizawa!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	143	7475	7332"
msgid "I haven't been wearing the\\r\n"
"Tojo badge for all that long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	131	7624	7493"
msgid "Truth be told, all I know about\\r\n"
"you are the stories, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	71	7745	7674"
msgid "But it was the chairman who\\r\n"
"was always telling them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	110	7885	7775"
msgid "He said it was his duty to protect\\r\n"
"the Tojo Clan you left to him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	8007	7947"
msgid "Aizawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	174	8263	8089"
msgid "The other execs don't want us having\\r\n"
"these talks with the Yamagasa Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	97	8389	8292"
msgid "Say they're not even in\\r\n"
"the same league as the Tojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	73	8485	8412"
msgid "How this equal alliance is anything but."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	199	8715	8516"
msgid "But the chairman took it all in stride\\r\n"
"because of what he promised you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	64	8871	8807"
msgid "So please, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	113	9006	8893"
msgid "Tell us where the chairman\\r\n"
"was going that night."
msgstr ""

